title: Ep212 Womb Raiders
description:
This week, the gals dig deep into some ultra-depraved kidnappings. Topics include a highly suspicious romantic liaison, the problem with an insanity defense, and one very, very bad friend. Put some of Winc's Golden Child Hard Cider in your cart, hide your car keys, and tune in for Womb Raiders.
